This paper discusses the use of WordNet and SUMO for commonsense reasoning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the analysis of knowledge resources, which could be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybersecurity (cs.CY).
